    "text": "Maldives is a South Asia country with a DC-type pension system centred on the Maldives Retirement Pension Scheme (MRPS). The system includes 2 schemes: Maldives Retirement Pension Scheme (MRPS), Old Age Basic Pension (OABP). The normal retirement age is 65 for both men and women. Contributions total 14.0% of insurable earnings (7.0% employee, 7.0% employer).",
